name: Lady of Nature
description:
"Lady of Nature is an artwork to show the process of healing from nature to the world.
When we feel the true vibe of a person just by being with them creat the Aura. Lady of Nature is inspired by Mother Earth. The lady of nature shown in the artwork is represent the environment. The leaf is a representation of climate change and the seasons of the year from different geographical areas. Hair of lady shows  atmosphere of the earth. A white snow blanket is shown for the peace and calmness we got from nature. This artwork is made to give positive vibes with a reminder of beautiful nature and its healing power. 
Love From Earth
